Function:
	Race_Set_ExitTime
Params:
	raceid - Race to set for.
	time - Time to set.
Return:
	-
Notes:
	Sets the time you are allowed out a vehicle before you
	fail the race.  0 means a vehicle exit is an instant fail.
	
